{"tid":17997,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"兩名年初二義士分別判刑21日及3個月","createTime":"2016-12-02T05:06:55.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-02T07:17:52.000Z","uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"65ea4afe766501c49170c7f9dd40f0ed3e01e817","tid":17997,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T05:06:55.000Z","msg":"農曆新年旺角發生的暴亂，男廚師和男補習教師分被指掟垃圾桶出馬路，以及襲擊兩名警員。兩人早前被裁定在公眾地方作擾亂秩序行為罪和一項襲警罪成立。首被告陳卓軒今於九龍城法院被判囚21天，次被告陳宇基則判囚3個月。 <br />\n<br />\n辯方替兩名被告申請保釋等候上訴，獲法庭批准。兩名被告分別以1萬港元保釋，期間不得離開香港。辯方求情時指，兩人為人不差，分別被扣留十多日，行為不算太嚴重，不會再犯事。 <br />\n<br />\n28歲任廚師的首被告陳卓軒被控今年2月9日(年初二)，在彌敦道將一個垃圾桶掟出馬路；20歲仍在求學但兼任補習教師的次被告陳宇基，則被指同日襲擊警長蔡國威及一位不知名警員。"},{"pid":"81185823e461e138e825c9eb1ec18cfbe209334f","tid":17997,"uid":4028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T05:07:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70f47dd22bb8336624d9d900f62b8bfd49b98dbd","tid":17997,"uid":34343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T05:22:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61d8d3fd82d3702b23b1d14b0768c35a730106a9","tid":17997,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T06:30:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"218f1e959ab49d9cc8bae4c6e4e0bb4b02de763b","tid":17997,"uid":38795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T06:51:14.000Z","msg":"陳宇基就係俾黑警打到流晒血訓係地下嗰個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a729678ad86e6e0c5e0054c66b7ee2d885cb2ac","tid":17997,"uid":25350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T07:03:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>陳宇基就係俾黑警打到流晒血訓係地下嗰個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockq